NG0114:1: thugs kyi dkyil 'khor rin chen sgo phye nas //
NG0114:2: bde gshegs dpal gyi mgur nas gsung bsgrags pa //
NG0114:3: gsang sngags rnal 'byor dbang phyug rgyal po yin //
NG0114:4: mnyam sbyor kun tu bzang po nyid kyi dbyings //
NG0114:5: rnam dag lam chen kun sgrol dgongs pa'i thugs //
NG0114:6: bgrod med rnal 'byor rdzogs pa chen po'i lam //
NG0114:7: byar med lhun rdzogs skye med chos kyi dbyings //
NG0114:8: theg pa'i rnam grangs gral thabs cha snyoms pa //
NG0114:9: ma 'dres chos rnams yongs su rdzogs pa'i rgyan //
NG0114:10: klung yangs rgya mtshor chu bo'i 'phro 'du bzhin //
NG0114:11: rgyal thabs spyi blugs dbang phyug rnams kyis mdzad //
NG0114:12: shes bya shes byed kun gyi gzhir gyur pa //
NG0114:13: kun gzhi gnas gyur rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor ni //
NG0114:14: rnam shes gdeng ka'i nam mkha'i rgyas mnyam pa //
NG0114:15: rtse mo byung rgyal bde ba chen po'i dbyings //
NG0114:16: sde rgyud yang thog bla na med pa yis //
NG0114:17: kun tu bzang po rang byung bcom ldan 'das //
NG0114:18: gcig tu rab tu che mchog chos kyi sku //
NG0114:19: lhun rdzogs sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgya che //
NG0114:20: bla na med pa'i go 'phang mchog la gnas //
NG0114:21: chos dbyings ma skyes sems can med pa'i phyir //
NG0114:22: srid pa'i chos rnams ye nas lhun gyis grub //
NG0114:24: mi gnas mya ngan 'das pa'i 'bras bur gnas //
NG0114:25: zla rgyas bzhin du spros pa mi mnga' ba //
NG0114:26: ye nas rgya mtsho 'khyil pa'i dbyings dang mtshungs //
NG0114:27: spros kyang de bzhin bsdus kyang de bzhin pa //
NG0114:28: bsod nams ye nas sku gsung thugs la rdzogs //
NG0114:29: lta ba nam mkha'i rgyal po'i 'phang gcod pa //
NG0114:30: btang snyoms chen po lhun rdzogs chos kyi dbyings //
NG0114:31: ma skyes mi gnas nam mkha'i rang bzhin las //
NG0114:32: thugs rje'i cho 'phrul ya mtshan chen por ston //
NG0114:33: khyung chen gshog rdzogs mkha' la lding ba bzhin //
NG0114:34: chu rlung ri brag gyen thur nyam mi nga *//
NG0114:35: bar snang nam mkha'i khams kun lam du bde //
NG0114:36: gang du dmigs pa'i sa kun gcod par byed //
NG0114:37: de bzhin ye nas blo sbyangs rnal 'byor thugs //
NG0114:38: byang chub snying por 'gro ba'i skal ldan po //
NG0114:39: sangs rgyas mngon du grub pa'i man ngag can //
NG0114:40: byang chub sems rtogs yon tan khyad par 'phags //
NG0114:41: bdag dang gzhan don lhun grub ma spangs pa //
NG0114:42: spyod pa rgya mtsho sna tshogs ci bder spyod //
NG0114:43: pad+ma skye ba'i rgyu ni 'dam yin te //
NG0114:44: pad+ma la yang 'dam gyis gos pa med //
NG0114:45: chos nyid chags pa med par rtogs gyur na //
NG0114:46: ye shes chags med nyams pa rdul tsam med //
NG0114:47: thugs rje spyod pa bsam yas ji snyed pa //
NG0114:48: rnal 'byor thabs kyis spyod pa ji bzhin spyod //
NG0114:49: rnam rtog spros bral gzung 'dzin mi mnga' ba //
NG0114:50: mkha' mnyam rgyal pos 'dod dgu'i re ba skong *//
NG0114:51: skye med dbyings las skye ba'i cho 'phrul rnams //
NG0114:54: mkha' dbyings rnam par dag pa'i dkyil 'khor ni //
NG0114:55: lhun grub yid bzhin rin chen gzhal yas khang *//
NG0114:56: phyogs dus kun nas 'khyil ba'i rgyal po'i tshogs //
NG0114:58: rgyal tshogs rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor rnams //
NG0114:59: 'gro don rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor bstan pa'i phyir //
NG0114:61: sprin med mkha' la skar tshogs rgyas pa bzhin //
NG0114:62: bkrag gsal longs spyod rdzogs pa'i 'khor dang bcas //
NG0114:63: kun bzang rdo rje sems dpa' dpal sbyor ba //
NG0114:64: shes rab dbyings nas thabs kyi phyag rgya gsal //
NG0114:65: sang nge sa le mnyam la ma 'dres pa //
NG0114:66: phung po khams dang skye mched rnal 'byor tshogs //
NG0114:67: kun tu bzang po rang byung bcom ldan 'das //
NG0114:68: gcig pu rab tu che mchog chos kyi sku //
NG0114:69: lhun rdzogs sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgya che //
NG0114:70: ye nas lhun grub byang chub snying por ni //
NG0114:71: bla med rgyal ba'i go 'phang mchog la bzhugs //
NG0114:72: bdag dang gzhan du rtog pa mi mnga' ba //
NG0114:73: 'jig rten rdo rje'i nyi ma shar ba bzhin //
NG0114:74: lhan ne lham mer ldan pa'i dkyil 'khor can //
NG0114:76: sku gsum ye shes drug dang chos kyi dbyings //
NG0114:77: ji ltar skar tshogs bzhin du ma 'phros kyang *//
NG0114:78: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor 'bar bas zil gyis gnon //
NG0114:79: de bzhin kun bzang rdo rje sems dpa' yang *//
NG0114:80: nyi ma stong gi gzi brjid 'bar bas brjid //
NG0114:81: rgyal ba'i tshogs chen 'dus pa'i gtso bo ste //
NG0114:82: phyi nang gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor kun gyi bdag /
NG0114:83: rnam par shes pa'i gtso bo kun gyi gzhi //
NG0114:84: rang byung ye shes dbyings las ma g.yos kyang *//
NG0114:85: stong khams yongs su snyoms pa'i thugs rje can //
NG0114:86: 'gro ba'i dpal mgon sna tshogs kun tu bzang *//
NG0114:87: dbye bsal blang dor gnyis med don du gcig /
NG0114:88: phyi dang nang kun thams cad chos kyi dbyings //
NG0114:89: rnam par thar pa'i spyod yul thams cad na //
NG0114:90: sangs rgyas sems can blang dor gnyis med de //
NG0114:91: lam dang gnyen pos bcos su ga la yod //
NG0114:92: bsgrub med rtsal sprugs smon pa med pa yi //
NG0114:93: byar med lhun rdzogs bde gshegs de bzhin te //
NG0114:94: rtog dpyod rnam dag gnyis med chos dbyings la //
NG0114:96: rtog dang mi rtog ye shes chos kyi sku //
NG0114:97: mthar thug med cing dbyings la bri ba med //
NG0114:98: skye med dbyings las skye ba'i cho 'phrul rnams //
NG0114:99: gang yang ma yin sna tshogs chos kyi dbyings //
NG0114:100: khams gsum rnam dag ma byung ma skyes na //
NG0114:101: dbus mtha' mi gzigs rnam par rtog las 'das //
NG0114:102: rnam rtog gnyan pos rnam par mi rtog pa //
NG0114:103: mi rtog 'dod pas rtog pa chen po yin //
NG0114:104: chos kyi dbyings nyid mi rtog mtha' las 'das //
NG0114:105: rtog dang mi rtog gnyis ka tshig gi @#//
NG0114:107: rnam rtog spros med byang chub snying po ni //
NG0114:108: kun gzhi rnam dag rnam shes rnam par dag /
NG0114:109: ye shes rnam dag chos dbyings rnam par dag /
NG0114:110: bdag nyid rnam dag gzhan yang rnam par dag /
NG0114:111: blta ba rnam dag spyod pa rnam par dag /
NG0114:112: sems can rnam dag sangs rgyas rnam par dag /
NG0114:113: rgyu rnams rnam dag 'bras bu rnam par dag /
NG0114:114: rten 'byung rnam dag 'brel pa rnam par dag /
NG0114:115: bdag med gnyis med byang chub snying po las //
NG0114:116: dbyings dang ye shes mnyam sbyor ma rtogs pa //
NG0114:118: rgyu 'bras don rtogs thabs dang shes rab ste //
NG0114:119: mkhyen pa mun sel byang chub sems dang mnyam //
NG0114:120: dkyil 'khor byang chub sems las rang byung ba //
NG0114:121: skye med 'gag med cho 'phrul sna tshogs 'byung *//
NG0114:122: mthun 'jug 'tshams pa'i spyod pa rgya mtsho ni //
NG0114:123: bdag dang gzhan don ye nas lhun grub kyang *//
NG0114:124: thugs rje chen pos 'gro don rdzogs par mdzad //
NG0114:125: ming tshig sgron mas don gyi gser mtshon pa //
NG0114:126: tshig gi rnam grangs gsung gi 'khor lo can //
NG0114:127: yod med mtha' las 'das pa'i kun gzhi ni //
NG0114:128: ming tshogs tshig gi rnam grangs sdud pa'i bdag /
NG0114:129: yod kyang ma yin de bzhin med ma yin //
NG0114:130: rtag pa ma yin chad pa'i mtha' ru min //
NG0114:131: bdag tu ma yin mtshan mar 'dzin pa med //
NG0114:132: phyi nang gzung 'dzin dngos por gang rtog pa //
NG0114:133: mi mkhas rmongs pa mu stegs lta la zhen //
NG0114:134: sna tshogs rang bzhin med par gang smra ba //
NG0114:135: med par mthong bas mu stegs chad pa'i lam //
NG0114:137: don gyi snying po'i bzhed las gol sar gsungs //
NG0114:138: gang yang ma yin sna tshogs chos kyi dbyings //
NG0114:139: bde gshegs rigs can byang chub snying po ni //
NG0114:140: gnyis med don rtogs rdzogs chen rnal 'byor pa'i //
NG0114:141: ye shes rnam dag lhun sbyor grub pa'i mtha' //
NG0114:142: re dogs med pas dbyings las dbyings nyid gsal //
NG0114:143: sangs rgyas gzhan nas tshol ba'i grub mtha' med //
NG0114:144: kun gzhi rnam shes ye nas chos kyi dbyings //
NG0114:145: ye nas lhun grub sangs rgyas mngon sum na //
NG0114:146: gang nas su la sangs rgyas gsol ba 'debs //
NG0114:147: 'khrul 'khor nyam thag ri dwags smig rgyu bzhin //
NG0114:148: sangs rgyas nyid kyis sangs rgyas nyid 'chos pa //
NG0114:149: rgya mtsho'i dbyings nas smig rgyur bsnyegs pa bzhin //
NG0114:150: de lta bas na sang rgyas thob 'dod na //
NG0114:151: ting 'dzin rgyal po byang chub sems la gsal //
NG0114:152: rtogs na bdag nyidasangs rgyas mngon sum ste //
NG0114:153: mnyam pa'i rgyal po gnyis med chos kyi sku //
NG0114:154: gsang dang gsang chen dkyil 'khor zhes bya ba //
NG0114:155: sangs rgyas dkyil 'khor rtogs pa nyid la 'dus //
NG0114:156: 'khor ldan bsod nams ye shes tshogs rdzogs pa //
NG0114:157: mngon sum mtshan dang dpe byad ldan pa yin //
NG0114:158: chos nyid 'dul dang snying rje chen po yi //
NG0114:160: rdzogs pa chen po'i dam tshig la //
NG0114:161: ye nas rnam dag byang chub snying po ni //
NG0114:163: mnyes ldan dngos grub blang med thob par nges //
NG0114:164: 'jig rten gsal byed nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor bzhin //
NG0114:165: grags ldan stong khams yongs su 'byung bar 'gyur //
NG0114:166: rgya mtsho u dum wa ra'i dpe bzhin du //
NG0114:167: byang chub sems ldan brgya'am lan cig na //
NG0114:168: mi dmigs ting 'dzin goms na 'grub par 'gyur //
NG0114:169: gal te chags sdang blang dor blo skyes te //
NG0114:170: 'khrul sems skad cig rkyen gyis khros 'gyur na //
NG0114:171: bla med byang chub don las 'gal ba'i phyir //
NG0114:172: skad cig ma las grub gyur sems 'di la //
NG0114:173: log rtog gsog zhugs khros pa'i dbang gis brlag /
NG0114:175: blo ldan nam zhig 'gyod pa drag skyes nas //
NG0114:176: rang sems dpang du btsug nas mi gtong ba //
NG0114:177: byang chub sems mchog blo la shar ba yin //
NG0114:178: bskal par bsags pa'i mun nag thibs po yang *//
NG0114:179: rigs pa'i rgyal po ye shes nyi zer gyis //
NG0114:181: mi shes blun rmongs skal med skye bo rnams //
NG0114:182: bdag dang gzhan du 'dzin pa'i sems rgyud kun //
NG0114:183: rang bzhin rgyal ba'i chos skur gcig pa las //
NG0114:184: 'khrul pas so sor rtags te mthong bas nor //
NG0114:185: ye shes sku la rgyal ba rgya mtsho dang *//
NG0114:186: log rtog sgyu ma rgyud lnga'i sems can rnams //
NG0114:187: kun rdzob sgyu mar khyad par bsam yas kyang *//
NG0114:188: don dam dbyings su rang bzhin yongs kyis mnyam //
NG0114:189: chos rnams thams cad ye nas stong pa'i phyir //
NG0114:191: sems can thams cad byang chub snying po la //
NG0114:192: rang gi sems nyid sangs rgyas mngon sum na //
NG0114:194: 'gro ba skal ldan rnams kyi don tsam du //
NG0114:195: bsgom zhing bsgrub pa'i tha snyad lung du bstan //
NG0114:196: de lta bas na mi 'grub pa yang med //
NG0114:197: de ltar de bzhin chos kyi dbyings rig na //
NG0114:198: ma rig rnams la snying rje chen po bskyed //
NG0114:199: snying rje skyes nas sgyu ma'i ting 'dzin gyis //
NG0114:200: 'gro don thabs la spyod pa sna tshogs ston //
NG0114:201: bdag dang gzhan du rtog pa med pa'i phyir //
NG0114:202: ye nas gnyis med don gcig chos kyi sku //
NG0114:203: chos sku skye med rtogs nas 'gro don du //
NG0114:204: skye ba'i cho 'phrul yang nas yang du bstan //
NG0114:205: mdzad pa bcu gnyis 'gro don mthar phyin pa //
NG0114:206: cir yang 'gyur ba'i gzugs can sprul pa'i sku //
NG0114:207: thugs rje cho 'phrul sna tshogs cir yang gsal //
NG0114:208: thugs rje'i sprul pas gdul bya kun 'dul bas //
NG0114:209: sgyu ma'i blo ldan rlom sems rdul tsam med //
NG0114:210: sangs rgyas rnams kyi dgongs rgyud ji lta bu //
NG0114:211: rang gi mtshan nyid ma bcos de bzhin nyid //
NG0114:212: chos rnams sgyu mar mngon sum gsal ba'i phyir //
NG0114:215: cir yang mi dmigs gang yang nges pa med //
NG0114:216: rang byung rmad grags byang chub snying po 'di //
NG0114:217: skye 'gro phyi nang gzugs rnams thams cad ni //
NG0114:218: sku mchog mi zad rgyan gyi 'khor lo rdzogs //
NG0114:219: sgra skad tha ma rab 'bring ma lus pa //
NG0114:220: gsung dbyangs mi zad rgyan gyi 'khor lo zab //
NG0114:221: thams cad ma lus dbyings su ro gcig phyir //
NG0114:222: thugs mchog mi zad rgyan gyi 'khor lor 'dus //
NG0114:223: mnyam sbyor thim 'gyur gsal nas mi mngon pa'i //
NG0114:224: chos kyi sku mchog byang chub snying por thim //
NG0114:225: gsang sngags dbang phyug go 'phang chen po 'dir //
NG0114:226: phyi nang gsang ba'i don dang mi ldan par //
NG0114:227: la la mkhas 'dod dregs pa'i nga rgyal can //
NG0114:228: rang gi lta ba ya rabs mthor bzhed de //
NG0114:229: gti mug dbang gis bag zon ma chags par //
NG0114:230: drag 'dod yas bzhag btsan thabs dregs pa yis //
NG0114:231: bdag la gzhan med dpe zla 'phags 'dod pa //
NG0114:232: gzhan la brnyas btsugs bdag gis lhar bsgoms kyang *//
NG0114:233: mnyam pa'i rgyal po'i don las 'gal ba'i phyir //
NG0114:234: lta spyod ya cha'i bdud kyi las su 'gyur //
NG0114:235: mtho dman rlom sems dbang gyur mnyam pa'i bcugs //
NG0114:236: nga'o snyam pa'i nga rgyal rang bzhin te //
NG0114:237: mkhas pa'i blo ldan bla ma'i lung bzhin du //
NG0114:238: skyon spong dge rtsa 'phags dral khyad par 'phags //
NG0114:239: tshig la mnyam sbyar mkhas pa zla med kyang *//
NG0114:240: dam tshig phyal pas byang chub sems spangs nas //
NG0114:241: rdo rjai lta bur 'grub 'gyur sems 'di la //
NG0114:242: log 'dren gsog can bden tshig ci smras kyang *//
NG0114:243: 'khrul pa'i sems nyid log 'dren dbang du 'gyur //
NG0114:244: gsang sngags rgya mtsho'i sgo 'di yangs pa ru //
NG0114:245: 'jug 'dod rgyal ba'i sku bslus slar log pa //
NG0114:246: bdud rtsi myangs nas dug tu 'khrul pa gang *//
NG0114:247: badzra yak+sha drag po snying la gnas //
NG0114:248: lus srog sgyu ma rdul du brlags nas kyang *//
NG0114:249: dmyal bar nges 'gro gtan du snying re rje //
NG0114:251: ri dwags mi yul so mtshams 'das dang 'dra //
NG0114:253: thams cad byang chub sems dpas rtse mo ste //
NG0114:254: mkhas pa'i thugs las byung bas byung rgyal nyid //
NG0114:255: byung rgyal nyid na rtse mo shar ba yang *//
NG0114:256: rnam grangs rgyan du bkod pas phreng ba ste //
NG0114:257: dbye bsal blang dor med pas dam pa'o //
NG0114:258: tshad med bzhi dang ldan pa'i rnam 'byor pa //
NG0114:259: bdag dang gzhan don bsgrub par brtson pa'i sems //
NG0114:260: sbyor sgrol dus ldan snying rje gnas rnams la //
NG0114:261: sems brod lung nod 'khor dang rdzas la sogs //
NG0114:262: phun sum tshogs 'dzin rgyal ba'i thugs rje can //
NG0114:263: dmigs pa'i don du rtse gcig khung ldan na //
NG0114:264: rnal 'byor che mchog grub pa'i rig 'dzin thob //
NG0114:265: snying rje med pa'i las kyi gzhi rnams ni //
NG0114:266: kun tu bzang po'i tshig tsam smra 'dra bas //
NG0114:269: kun tu bzang mor sbyor ldan dngos grub can //
NG0114:270: rnal 'byor grub pa'i phrin las rgya mtsho rnams //
NG0114:271: skye med don dam kun rdzob rnam par spangs //
NG0114:272: theg chen spyi blugs rang bzhin rnal 'byor don //
NG0114:273: lhun grub rdzogs chen sa rnams kun gyi bla //
NG0114:274: de ltar shes ldan bdud bzhi rnam par spangs //
NG0114:275: sdig 'dzem cher bskyed bsod nams khri phrag yas //
NG0114:276: lta ba dgongs pa'i 'bras bu mthar phyin par //
NG0114:277: lung dang man ngag nges don gsal bar bya //
NG0114:279: sems med ma skyes don med bral ba yin //
NG0114:282: bcom ldan 'das te ma lus kun gyi dpal //
NG0114:283: thugs rje thabs kyi 'gro don mthar phyin pa //
NG0114:284: bde ba thams cad mkhyen pa nyid kyi ngang *//
NG0114:285: sku gsung thugs kyi rang bzhin chos kyi dbyings //
NG0114:286: byang chub sems kyi srog gi 'khor lo 'di //
NG0114:287: mnyam nyid 'dus pa'i gter la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0114:288: lus ngag yid gsum sku gsung thugs sbyor ba //
NG0114:289: rgyal ba rnams kyi gsang chen 'khor bzlog pa //
NG0114:290: mya ngan 'das pa'i dam tshig lu gu rgyud //
NG0114:291: chos dbyings rnal 'byor yongs kyi gter chen pas //
NG0114:292: rna brgyud thugs kyi gter chen skal ldan la //
NG0114:293: mi nub yongs kyi btsas su bzhag pa yin //
NG0114:294: sku gsung thugs las bsdus pa'i snying po 'di //
NG0114:295: dus gsum rgyal ba'i chos dbyings sku gsung thugs //
NG0114:296: mnyam nyid 'gro don man ngag kun gyi gter //
NG0114:297: skal ldan tshad ma rang rig dbang phyug gis //
NG0114:298: de yi rjes sob thugs kyi sras mchog la //
NG0114:299: tsit+ta'i dkyil 'khor yangs par gsal gyur cing *//
NG0114:300: chos dbyings skye med mi gnas mya ngan 'das med dag /
NG0114:301: mi skye mi 'gag 'khor ba spang len med //
NG0114:302: nga med bdag dang bral ba rgyal ba'i thugs //
NG0114:303: rnal 'byor gsang ba'i snying po bsam yas pa //
NG0114:304: rin chen gter 'dus rgyal bas brjod mi lang *//
NG0114:305: ma spangs ma bsgrubs nam mkha'i ngang du gnas //
NG0114:306: khams gsum brtags na 'khor ba mya ngan med //
NG0114:307: phyogs char bcas na bde gshegs snying po min //
NG0114:308: kun gyi rang bzhin 'ja' tshon snang bzhin med //
NG0114:309: de la med bzhin 'byung ba rgya mtsho 'dra //
NG0114:310: chos dbyings skye ba med pa yum gyi ngang *//
NG0114:311: rgyal ba'i phyag rgya rgyal ba'i cho 'phrul can //
NG0114:312: 'khor ba mya ngan 'das la dgod pa'i phyir //
NG0114:313: rang byung ye shes dbyings las ma g.yos kyang *//
NG0114:314: stong khams yongs la snyoms pa'i thugs rje 'byung *//
NG0114:315: nga med bdag dang bral ba'i snying po rdzogs //
NG0114:316: don dam ye shes dbyings 'di rdzogs pa che //
NG0114:317: snying po nyi ma bzhin te 'od kyi mchog /
NG0114:318: skye 'gro phyi nang gzugs rnams thams cadani *//
NG0114:319: sku mchog mi zad rgyan gyi 'khor lor rdzogs //
NG0114:320: sgra skad tha ma rab 'bring ma lus pa //
NG0114:321: gsung mchog mi zad rgyan gyi 'khor lor rdzogs //
NG0114:322: dbyer med don dam dbyings su ro gcig @#//
NG0114:324: thugs mchog mi zad rgyan 'khor yongs su rdzogs //
NG0114:325: thams cad sku gsung thugs te dbyer med pa //
NG0114:326: skye med nam mkha'i klong yangs rgya mtsho bzhin //
NG0114:327: 'du 'bral med pa'i dbyings mchog rab 'byams na //
NG0114:328: chen po bzhi yi cho 'phrul grangs med pa //
NG0114:329: brtags sam rtogs na 'byung ba'i 'bras bur 'dus //
NG0114:330: 'chi ba med pa'i sman chen bdud rtsi 'di //
NG0114:331: ye nas rdzogs pas gzhan nas btsal mi dgos //
